  "body": "At version[b529d47]:\r\nIf a proposer of a block doesn't verify the attestation's target root or beacon_block_root when packing,  some of the packed attestations can be with:\r\n1)invalid  target roots\r\n2)or (and) invalid beacon_block_roots\r\n\r\nThen the state by the block will be with invalid attestations, while the attesters and the proposer can still:\r\n1) be rewarded because of matching sources/matching targets(if only beacon_block_root is invalid)/inclusion bonus.\r\n2) avoid penalties.",
